---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Capabilities | LEGEND INDUSTRIES">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-200 pb-5">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Capabilities</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">This page defines what the business can and cannot handle in bulk requirement contexts.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-5 text-slate-800">
      <p>
        Legend Industries operates as a manufacturing-backed supplier for bulk utility merchandise with customization support.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">Categories handled</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
          <li>Bags</li>
          <li>Bottles</li>
          <li>Diaries</li>
          <li>Utility merchandise</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">Customization methods (high-level)</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
          <li>Printing</li>
          <li>Engraving</li>
          <li>Requirement-specific branding methods based on material suitability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>
        Engagement scope is requirement-driven. Pricing, materials, and production details are finalized through discussion after requirement clarity.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-700">
      For engagement sequence details, refer to <a class="underline underline-offset-4" href="/process">Process</a>. For qualified enquiries,
      refer to <a class="underline underline-offset-4" href="/contact">Contact</a>.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
